"#\"><strong>Properties</strong></a>\n  <ol>\n   <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid\">grid</a></li>\n   <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-area\">grid-area</a></li>\n   <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-auto-columns\">grid-auto-columns</a></li>\n   <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-auto-flow\">grid-auto-flow</a></li>\n   <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-auto-rows\">grid-auto-rows</a></li>\n   <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-column\">grid-column</a></li>\n   <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-column-end\">grid-column-end</a></li>\n   <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-column-gap\">grid-column-gap</a></li>\n   <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-column-start\">grid-column-start</a></li>\n   <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-gap\">grid-gap</a></li>\n   <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-row\">grid-row</a></li>\n   <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-row-end\">grid-row-end</a></li>\n   <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-row-gap\">grid-row-gap</a></li>\n   <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-row-start\">grid-row-start</a></li>\n   <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-template\">grid-template</a></li>\n   <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-template-areas\">grid-template-areas</a></li>\n   <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-template-columns\">grid-template-columns</a></li>\n   <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-template-rows\">grid-template-rows</a></li>\n  </ol>\n </li>\n <li data-default-state=\"open\"><a href=\"#\"><strong>Glossary</strong></a>\n  <ol>\n   <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Glossary/Grid_lines\">Grid lines</a></li>\n   <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Glossary/Grid_tracks\">Grid tracks</a></li>\n   <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Glossary/Grid_cell\">Grid cell</a></li>\n   <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Glossary/Grid_areas\">Grid areas</a></li>\n   <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Glossary/Gutters\">Gutters</a></li>\n   <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Glossary/Grid_rows\">Grid row</a></li>\n   <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Glossary/Grid_column\">Grid column</a></li>\n  </ol>\n </li>\n</ol>\n","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p><strong><code>grid-gap</code></strong>&nbsp; ist die <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/Shorthand_properties\">shorthand</a> CSS Eigenschaft für&nbsp; <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/row-gap\"><code>grid-row-gap</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> und <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/column-gap\"><code>grid-column-gap</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> , welche die Spalten (gutter) zwischen Rasterreihen und Rasterspalten festlegt.</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: css no-line-numbers notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token comment\">/* Ein &lt;Länge&gt; Wert */</span>\n<span class=\"token property\">grid-gap</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 20px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token property\">grid-gap</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 1em<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token property\">grid-gap</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 3vmin<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token property\">grid-gap</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 0.5cm<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">/* Ein &lt;Prozent&gt; Wert */</span>\n<span class=\"token property\">grid-gap</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 16%<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token property\">grid-gap</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 100%<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">/* Zwei &lt;Länge&gt; Werte */</span>\n<span class=\"token property\">grid-gap</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 20px 10px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token property\">grid-gap</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 1em 0.5em<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token property\">grid-gap</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 3vmin 2vmax<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token property\">grid-gap</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 0.5cm 2mm<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">/* Ein or zwei &lt;Prozent&gt; Werte */</span>\n<span class=\"token property\">grid-gap</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 16% 100%<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token property\">grid-gap</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 21px 82%<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">/* Globale Werte */</span>\n<span class=\"token property\">grid-gap</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> inherit<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token property\">grid-gap</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> initial<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token property\">grid-gap</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> unset<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n\n<p><table class=\"properties\"><tbody><tr><th scope=\"row\"><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/CSS/initial_value\">Initialwert</a></th><td>wie die jeweiligen Kurzschreibweisen:<br><ul><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/CSS/row-gap\"><code>row-gap</code></a>: <code>normal</code></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/CSS/column-gap\"><code>column-gap</code></a>: <code>normal</code></li></ul></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Anwendbar auf</th><td>multi-column elements, flex containers, grid containers</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\"><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/CSS/inheritance\">Vererbt</a></th><td>Nein</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\"><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/CSS/computed_value\">Berechneter Wert</a></th><td>wie die jeweiligen Kurzschreibweisen:<br><ul><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/CSS/row-gap\"><code>row-gap</code></a>: as specified, with &lt;length&gt;s made absolute, and normal computing to zero except on multi-column elements</li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/CSS/column-gap\"><code>column-gap</code></a>: as specified, with &lt;length&gt;s made absolute, and normal computing to zero except on multi-column elements</li></ul></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Animationstyp</th><td>wie die jeweiligen Kurzschreibweisen:<br><ul><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/CSS/row-gap\"><code>row-gap</code></a>: <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/CSS/length#interpolation\">Längenangabe</a>, <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/CSS/percentage#interpolation\">Prozentsatz</a> oder <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/CSS/calc\"><code>calc()</code></a>;</li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/CSS/column-gap\"><code>column-gap</code></a>: <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/CSS/length#interpolation\">Längenangabe</a>, <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/CSS/percentage#interpolation\">Prozentsatz</a> oder <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/CSS/calc\"><code>calc()</code></a>;</li></ul></td></tr></tbody></table></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"Syntax","isH3":false,"content":"<p>Dieser Eigenschaft wird ein Wert für&nbsp;<code>&lt;'grid-row-gap'&gt;</code>&nbsp;zugeordnet, gefolgt von einem optionalen Wert für&nbsp;<code>&lt;'grid-column-gap'&gt;</code>. Falls&nbsp;<code>&lt;'grid-column-gap'&gt;</code>&nbsp;ausgelassen wird, wird diesem der gleiche Wert zugeordnet wie&nbsp;<code>&lt;'grid-row-gap'&gt;</code>.</p>\n\n<p><code>&lt;'grid-row-gap'&gt;</code>&nbsp;und <code>&lt;'grid-column-gap'&gt;</code> werden jeweils angegeben als&nbsp;<code>&lt;Länge&gt;</code> or als&nbsp;<code>&lt;Prozent&gt;</code>.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"werte","title":"Werte","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"länge\"><code>&lt;Länge&gt;</code></dt>\n <dd>Gibt die Breite der Spalte an, welche die Grid-Linien trennt.</dd>\n <dt id=\"prozent\"><code>&lt;Prozent&gt;</code></dt>\n <dd>Ist die prozentuale Breite der Lücke zwischen zwei Rasterlinien im Verhältnis zu der Gesamtgröße des Elements.</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"formale_syntax","title":"Formale Syntax","isH3":true,"content":"<pre class=\"notranslate\"><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/CSS/row-gap\" title=\"normal | <length-percentage>\">&lt;'row-gap'&gt;</a> <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/CSS/column-gap\" title=\"normal | <length-percentage>\">&lt;'column-gap'&gt;</a><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/CSS/Value_definition_syntax#fragezeichen_()\" title=\"Fragezeichen: Die Entität ist optional\">?</a></pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"beispiel","title":"Beispiel","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"html_inhalt","title":"HTML Inhalt","isH3":true,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">id</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>grid<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span></code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"css_inhalt","title":"CSS Inhalt","isH3":true,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: css; highlight[5] notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token selector\">#grid</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">display</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> grid<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">height</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 200px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">grid-template</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token function\">repeat</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>3<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> 1fr<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> / <span class=\"token function\">repeat</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>3<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> 1fr<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">grid-gap</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 20px 5px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token selector\">#grid &gt; div</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">background-color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> lime<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n\n<p><iframe class=\"sample-code-frame\" title=\"CSS Inhalt\" id=\"frame_example\" width=\"100%\" height=\"200px\" src=\"https://yari-demos.prod.mdn.mozit.cloud/de/docs/Web/CSS/gap/_sample_.example.ht